               <p>parson—I apprehended him, and attended the trial as a witness—I produce the Certificate of his conviction-(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I have minded my work ever since, only my master was very slack—I worked at Mr. Christie's glass works, Westminster.</p>
